          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method is called to give a widget an opportunity to update its contents and redraw its view prior to an operation such as a snapshot. When the widget is finished updating its contents (and redrawing, if necessary), the widget should call the completion handler block, passing the appropriate "
